    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a project or a source for parts. While it currently runs, the engine is showing significant wear, and the transmission requires immediate attention. The exterior has several large dents and noticeable rust spots, and the interior shows heavy use with torn upholstery and some non-functional electronics. Please expect to invest time and money into repairs if you plan to make this a reliable driver again.",
